content:
Aajnya moolam yeehoodyaayil sarvvanmaarum
Per chaartthumpollaa sarkkaarudyogasthhanmaar
Mariyaamnaathhan yauseppin pakkal chennothi
Nee daaveedinnooril poyi perekenam.
Svantamdesham bhoopan vannoraaneratthil
Thanne bodhichelpaanaayi thayyaaraayi.
Mannanmaaril mannanthanne peri baala
Yauseppum chernnerippoyaall bethalahemil.
